<para id="element-129">
<term>Solution : </term> 
We shall first calculate relative velocity in horizontal and vertical directions and then combine them to find the resultant relative velocity. Let "x" and "y" axes be in horizontal and perpendicular directions. In x-direction,


</para>
<para id="element-130">
<m:math display="block">
